About 20 school children have been rushed to hospital due to suspected food poisoning on Wednesday.&#8220;About 20 school children have been admitted in Chris Hani Baragwana Hospital for suspected food poisoning at a Primary school in the Hills,&#8221; ER24 spokesperson Russel Meiring said.According to reports, the children had been complaining about abdominal pains. They were rushed to Florida and Baragwanath Hospitals for further care.More to follow&#8230;